Create a virtual machine with docker-machine using the virtualbox driver, and
named Char.

1. Get Brew: git clone https://github.com/Homebrew/brew ~/.linuxbrew/Homebrew
	Use eval $(~/.linuxbrew/bin/brew shellenv) to start the brew service
	brew install docker docker-machine

2. https://docs.docker.com/machine/get-started/
	docker-machine create --driver virtualbox Char
	docker-machine ls

	Use to restart containers:
	docker-machine start Char